txt.en: Defeat many Orcs and Uruk-hai in Southern Mirkwood.
Defeat Orcs and Uruk-hai in Southern Mirkwood

Your assistance to the Elves of the Mirkwood Offensive in their war against Dol Guldur shall earn you great favour amongst the Galadhrim. The cruel Orcs and Uruk-hai prowl in greater and greater numbers throughout Middle-earth these days, and there is certainly no lack of these foes in Mirkwood, but the forest has been made a little safer by your hand.
